### Bluetooth
load-module module-bluetooth-policy
load-module module-bluetooth-discover

### CamillaDSP - set ALSA Loopback as default sink
### module-udev-detect auto-detects the Loopback card as alsa_output.platform-snd_aloop.0.analog-stereo
set-default-sink alsa_output.platform-snd_aloop.0.analog-stereo
